children.text: Launched in Spring 2019, RED CLUB x Cartier officially kicks off its celebration of building connections between young entrepreneurs from across the globe. Established by Cartier, RED CLUB x Cartier is a community that connects global young entrepreneurs who have strong ties with Asia and who aim at having a positive impact on society through their businesses.

Initially launched in France, Italy and in the United Kingdom, RED CLUB x Cartier seeks out audacious entrepreneurs who either come from Asia or have a strong relationship with Asia. As a community, RED CLUB x Cartier encourages these entrepreneurs to connect with each other beyond their individual organizations, and mutually share their experience of starting, funding, and running a business, with the common denominator of their deep connection with Asia. As RED CLUB x Cartier successfully grows, the community has extended to Russia and Japan in 2021.
As of today, Red Club x Cartier welcomes 19 members from 5 countries from a broad range of industries: Food, Fashion, Energy, Technology, Blockchain etc.
